<h3 style="text-align: center;"><img src="https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/761715370838458408/971962058268606484/About-section.png" alt="" width="400" height="59" /></h3>
<p style="text-align: center;"><strong>Swappage </strong>is a <span style="text-decoration: underline;">Bedwars1058 addon</span> that <em>introduces</em> the <strong>Swappage </strong>gamemode; which is on <strong>Hypixel</strong>'s Bedwars Swappage Idea.<br /><br /><strong>Swappage </strong>is a fun, but very confusing gamemode where your team will swap with your opponent's team. Your goal is to win the game amidst the challenges that you will encounter.</p>
<p style="text-align: center;">&nbsp;</p>
<h3 style="text-align: center;"><img src="https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/761715370838458408/971962559576043610/Features-Section.png" alt="" /></h3>
<ul style="text-align: center;">
<li style="text-align: center;">Per-arena swappage support.</li>
<li style="text-align: center;">Game rejoining support.</li>
<li style="text-align: center;">Performance friendly.</li>
<li style="text-align: center;">Supports 1.8.8-1.18.4 versions.</li>
<li style="text-align: center;">PlaceholderAPI support (coming soon).</li>
<li style="text-align: center;">Extensive discord support.</li>
<li style="text-align: center;">100% messages customizability.</li>
</ul>
